include/sync_replica_sql_with_primary.inc

We now stop the IO thread and ensure that the relaylog files
are not deleted on doing a change primary with a running SQL thread.

include/stop_replica_io.inc
CHANGE PRIMARY TO PRIMARY_HEARTBEAT_PERIOD= 10;
include/assert.inc [The relaylog file should not change if change primary command was executed while SQL thread was running.]

We now stop the SQL thread and ensure that the relaylog files
are not deleted on doing a change primary with a running IO thread.

include/stop_replica_sql.inc
include/start_replica_io.inc
CHANGE PRIMARY TO PRIMARY_DELAY= 20;
include/assert.inc [The relaylog file should not change if change primary command was executed while IO thread was running.]

If the relay_log_file and relay_log_pos options are used, we dont purge
relaylogs.

include/stop_replica_io.inc
CHANGE PRIMARY TO RELAY_LOG_FILE= 'RELAY_LOG_FILE';
CHANGE PRIMARY TO RELAY_LOG_POS= RELAY_LOG_POS;
include/assert.inc [The relaylog file should not change if change primary command contained relay_log_file or relay_log_pos option.]

With both the threads stopped and no use of relay_log_file or
relay_log_pos options, the relaylogs should be deleted.

CHANGE PRIMARY TO PRIMARY_HEARTBEAT_PERIOD= 20;
include/assert.inc [With both the threads stopped and no use of relay_log_file or relay_log_pos options in change primary command, the relaylogs should be deleted.]

cleanup

